{"tid":1798906,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"張華峰提「聖誕」：X你老母","createTime":"2019-12-26T14:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T19:22:20.000Z","uid":58867,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d626608d66280b3c7a16b9c9f7542665063e0bf2","tid":1798906,"uid":58867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:37:46.000Z","msg":"聖誕前各公司互送聖誕卡、果籃，聊表心意，不過立法會議員張華峰對「聖誕」就有HardFeeling，《壹週刊》報道，張華峰一聽到「聖誕」無名火起：「我最憎就是聖誕！」，細個因為屋企窮，無錢買聖誕卡買，所以他將人哋送畀佢張聖誕卡，改咗自己個名送畀人，點知麥美娟將件事唱通街，超慘！仲話，「我已經同佢反左面架喇！」<br />\n<br />\n依家張華峰財力雄厚，想送幾多果籃塞住人哋把口都得啦！佢話雖然收大把果籃，但一個都唔會送出去，仲好激動咁話，「你咪唔好同我做生意囉，笨！我X你老母」嚇到個記者打咗個突，童年的影響之大，真係唔講得笑！"},{"pid":"066fd53742dcb3ac1afe11005959da05e9995c25","tid":1798906,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:38:24.000Z","msg":"改啲唔改啲"},{"pid":"b648c553ddfc392cd664c5a08b73da7da364c5a4","tid":1798906,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:40:53.000Z","msg":"&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"c1925c197059f9acf14115877a72cfa1467d62d1","tid":1798906,"uid":337555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:41:29.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e504f5564e01b5853139e0a2c7e9ea4537ea248b","tid":1798906,"uid":117422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:41:33.000Z","msg":"改文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e89fe85264b38c9cea52c984abb8ada283a5767","tid":1798906,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnYKeWt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtnYKeWt.jpg&h=0f34dcbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5efc93beef08e994b7ec332bb6038c879caa51bf","tid":1798906,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T19:22:20.000Z","msg":"監警會副主席張華峰﹕速龍小隊處理衝突不必展示編號　「點解要畀你投訴我行為是否過分？」<br />